about.summary: Easily access song lyrics in a tidy way.

name: r-genius
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '2.2.0' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-genius
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/genius_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/genius/genius_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 9b62b9d60605edf7a5e40f8eec026055f1d24bd2a7acc825552b53e6f979c200

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 2
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-dplyr >=0.7.0
    - r-purrr
    - r-readr
    - r-reshape2
    - r-rvest
    - r-stringr
    - r-tibble
    - r-tidyr
    - r-tidytext
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-dplyr >=0.7.0
    - r-purrr
    - r-readr
    - r-reshape2
    - r-rvest
    - r-stringr
    - r-tibble
    - r-tidyr
    - r-tidytext

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('genius')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('genius')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/josiahparry/genius
  license: GPL-2
  summary: Easily access song lyrics in a tidy way.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r

# Package: genius

# Description: Easily access song lyrics in a tidy way.
